---
const year = 2026;
---
<footer class="mt-24 text-sm" style="border-top:1px solid rgba(120,255,180,0.16)">
  <div class="wrap py-12 grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-3">
    <div>
      <div class="font-display font-extrabold text-text"><span class="green">~/</span>ide<span class="amber">eea</span>s</div>
      <p class="mt-3 text-fog max-w-xs leading-relaxed">
        A growing library of validated startup and side-project ideas, demand, difficulty, money, and a starter stack for each.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="amber mb-3"># explore</div>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-fog">
        <li><a href="/ideas/" class="hover:text-text transition-colors">all idea collections</a></li>
        <li><a href="/how-to-validate-a-startup-idea/" class="hover:text-text transition-colors">how to validate an idea</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about/" class="hover:text-text transition-colors">about ideeeas</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="amber mb-3"># weekly drop</div>
      <p class="text-fog mb-3">10 validated ideas in your inbox every week.</p>
      <a href="/#subscribe" class="btn-term inline-block px-3 py-1.5">[ subscribe free ]</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="rule"></div>
  <div class="wrap py-5 text-xs text-fog/80 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-2 justify-between">
    <span><span class="green">$</span> echo "© {year} ideeeas. ideas are starting points, validate before you build."</span>
    <span>// some outbound tool links may be affiliate links</span>
  </div>
</footer>
